verbose_text: Similarly, immunoblot analyses of mouse embryonic fibroblasts (MEFs) isolated from Rhbdf2 +/+ and Rhbdf2 P159L / P159L mice also revealed enhanced EGFR signaling as demonstrated by reduced EGFR protein levels (due to downregulation of sustained EGFR receptor activation), and by enhanced protein levels of phospho-AKT, phospho-ERK1/2 and phospho-S6 in Rhbdf2 P159L / P159L MEFs compared with those of Rhbdf2 +/+ mice (XREF_FIG B).
